snippet.title: Lynne Sater
snippet.description: Sater, Lynne (Nee Engfer) Age 49, died October 24, 2011, at her Oconomowoc, WI home, surrounded by her loving family, following a nearly two year battle with bile duct cancer. Lynne is survived by her husband, Terry, daughters Savannah, Autumn, and Sierra, parents John and Virginia Engfer of Jordan,
